metadata.name: Trapped In My Own Mind
metadata.description:
The world constantly spins, never waiting a second for me to catch up. I try to comprehend what's going on from time to time. My thoughts seem to cloud my judgment, creating a space of emptiness.    

In my head, I've created a perception of myself, perhaps the person who I want to be. Chaotic and colorful but, for now, only conceptual. Maybe, one day they'll come out and truly appreciate the world. Until then, I'm just â€¦ 

Trapped In My Own Mind
